title: Star Citizen Jump Point issue 3
description:
This is Jump Point issue #3 from Roberts Space Industries (Star Citizen), It's only available to subscribers currently.

Not everyone can afford the 10$ / month, so here it is, enjoy this 39 page PDF!

If you have never heard of Roberts Space Industries or Star Citizen, I highly suggest you check out Robertsspaceindustries.com 

It's a Space-Sim fan's wet dream, being made by the one and only Chris Roberts.


If you enjoy the content and want to further support CIG (the developer) please consider subscribing for a month or two.

Enjoy!
